                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipits and headings of the texts;
                           directives for the ministers and their abbreviations; elements of
                           punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.
 On the incipit
                           page of Texts I, III-4, III-6 (fols. 2r, 65v, 83v), few lines are
                           rubricated (alternating with black lines).
